org.apache.flex.abc.visitors

Interface IFlowGraphVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FrameCountVisitor, FrameModelEncoder

    public interface IFlowGraphVisitor
    A IFlowGraphVisitor defines the behavior of a visitor over a control flow graph.
